{"type": "article", "id": 11412, "title": "英国古德伍德速度节，全世界最快的车都来了", "description": "所谓的车迷狂欢，是指你可以摸得到梦幻座驾的那种。", "date": "2015-06-30T09:15:04Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 12167, "name": "Goodwood"}, {"id": 12168, "name": "Lotus Cars"}, {"id": 12169, "name": "Talbot-Lago"}], "category": 17, "author": 26306, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 73, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702132545xRY1AJlhw6DGZsai.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span>古德伍德，是位于英国西</span><span><span>塞萨克斯郡</span></span><span>的特色小镇。这里有世界闻名的赛马场、古德伍德复古艺术节、古德伍德咖啡艺术节，还有世界上规模最大、历史最悠久的赛车盛事古德伍德速度节。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>“假如你是一名</span><span><span>汽车</span></span><span>发烧友，那么古德伍德便是你的圣地。”红牛车队首席技术执行官安德里亚</span><span>·</span><span>纽维曾这样形容。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132538XvuJ3tWdZ5n1IGYE.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" height=\"400\" width=\"640\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span>上周末，这项一年一度的车迷狂欢在古德</span><span>伍德开幕，</span><span>今年的主题是“马力全开无所畏惧：极限边缘的赛车”。<span></span>梅赛德斯、红牛、<span></span></span><span><span>法拉利</span></span><span>、</span><span><span>迈凯伦</span></span><span>和威<span></span>廉姆斯五家顶级 <span>F1 </span>一级方程式车队携最新的赛车前来，现役 <span>F1 </span>车手马萨和莱科宁也来到现场。<span></span> <br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132538yB8hEpMAXrYLdJ92.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" height=\"480\" width=\"640\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span>(</span><span>迈凯轮车手简森</span><span>·</span><span>巴顿成为了古德伍德的熟面孔</span><span>)</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132539ZOHXKivMDB925x1a.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" height=\"427\" width=\"640\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span>布鲁克兰围场展示的是赛车家族系列中的经典车型，在这里游客们可以近距离欣赏到这些传奇车型的工艺细节。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132539EUve1CQm6a0x2sJr.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" height=\"427\" width=\"640\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132540PAWNFwLjU2sZh9q0.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" height=\"627\" width=\"940\" data-ratio=\"0.66702128\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132540nXvgfq2BGplAcrLM.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" height=\"427\" width=\"640\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>每年的卡地亚“豪华风格”汽车设计竞赛单位将评选出当届速度节上最为唯美、奢华的跑车。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132541xOTSzBmMalsfvAyj.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" height=\"383\" width=\"640\" data-ratio=\"0.5984375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t今年获胜的是 1937 年款 Talbot-Lago T150-C S Teardrop 天使之泪，其美艳的程度简直让人落泪。以下为其他获奖作品：\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span>Sweeping Statements</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span>1939 Delahaye 165 Cabriolet\r\n(Peter Mullin)</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132541g1QPm4vOxouaLzlw.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" height=\"427\" width=\"640\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span>Modern Classics</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span>2011 Eagle Speedster\r\n(Henry Pearman)</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132542Q1JSZMGyrYx4HOB3.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" height=\"421\" width=\"640\" data-ratio=\"0.6578125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span>A Sporting Advantage</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>1931\r\nAlfa Romeo  8C 2300MM (Eric Heerema)</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132542FxvJZtlmWHb2N1Re.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" height=\"426\" width=\"640\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>Goddess of the Highway<br>\r\n1957 Citroën DS19 Berline (Wenzel Gelpke)</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132543ATnEwQ0DbSpCxORJ.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" height=\"426\" width=\"640\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>英国跑车与赛车生产商路特斯，或译作莲花汽车 <span>(Lotus\r\nCars)</span> 也是古德伍德的常客，素来以纯粹的驾驶乐趣和轻量化的设计闻名。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132543mZkYQ4PGVTI9M0aq.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" height=\"426\" width=\"640\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>本次速度节，发布了一款新车型—— “<span>three-eleven</span>” ，是目前莲花旗下最快的跑车，预计明年二月交付，限量生产 <span>311</span> 部，售价约为 <span>82,000</span> 英镑起。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><span> </span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021325444krPfQO0JXDyKC8t.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" height=\"426\" width=\"640\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><span>three-eleven</span> 使用超轻量化车身，座舱无顶棚设计极为纯粹，采用由碳纤维复合材料制造的轻桶形座椅。出色的功率<span>-</span>重量比使得它能够在<span> 3 </span>秒内完成 <span>0-100 km/h </span>的加速，极速则可达<span> 290km/h</span>。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132544x6RJQaBVIyFqfXpK.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" height=\"426\" width=\"640\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t无挡风设计则流露出肆无忌惮的姿态，毫无疑问，驾驶者需要一个头盔才可以驾驭激进的 three-eleven，以此抵挡冲向面部的高速气流。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t(图片来自 grrc.goodwood.com)<br>\r\n<span><span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n"}